content.text:
Perfect! Now I have all the information needed. Let me create a comprehensive summary for the user.

---

## Points Screen Structure

### File Structure
```
/src/screens/Points/
├── index.tsx          # Hook component (logic)
├── view.tsx           # Render component
├── Models/index.ts    # TypeScript types
└── data/index.ts      # Data mappings (icon mappings, key names)
```

### Store Dependencies (useRootStore)

The Points screen uses these store slices:

1. **pointsProducts** (via `usePoints` hook)
   - `products: PointsProduct[]`
   - `status: PointsProductsStatus`

2. **pointsBalance** (via `usePoints` hook)
   - `points: number`
   - `status: PointsBalanceStatus`

3. **parameterPointsProgram** (via `LearnMorePointsSection`)
   - `data: ParameterPointsProgramResponse[]`
   - `status: ParameterPointsProgramStatus`
   - `pointsQuantity: number`
   - `conversionFactor: number`

### Design System Components Used

From `@semparar/design-system-app`:
- `Box`
- `CardPoints`
- `CardMiddle`
- `CardActivity`
- `Text`
- `BackDropBottom` (via PointsInfoBottomSheet)
- `Button` (via PointsInfoBottomSheet)

### Navigation Dependencies

- `useFocusEffect` from `@react-navigation/native`
- Routes: `MyOrdersRewardProgram`, `Home`, `ExtractRewardProgram`, `InvoiceCashbackPoints`, `InvoiceCashbackOnboarding`, `RewardProgramMarketplace`, `AirlineMilesMarketplace`, `LearnMoreRewardProgram`

---

## Key Code Content for Storybook Story

### 1. Main Types (Models/index.ts)

```typescript
export interface PointsCardItem {
  id: number;
  text: string;
  bgColor: string;
  icon: string;
  textAlign: string;
  iconColor: string;
  onPress: () => void;
}

export interface PointsViewProps {
  isLoadingBalance: boolean;
  handleGoBack: () => void;
  pointsAvailable?: number;
  pointsOptions?: PointsProduct[];
  items?: PointsCardItem[];
  pointsHasError?: boolean;
  handleNavigateToInvoiceCashback?: () => void;
  onOpenExtract: () => void;
  onOpenDefault: () => void;
  modalizeRef: RefObject<PropsModalizeRef>;
  onMenuPress: () => void;
  isMyOrders: boolean;
  setIsMyOrders: (value: boolean) => void;
  handlerGoHome: () => void;
  handleMyOrders: () => void;
}
```

### 2. Data Mappings (data/index.ts)

```typescript
export const KEY_NAME_TO_ICON = {
  RESCUE_IN_INVOICE: 'cashback na fatura',
  MARKETPLACE: 'shopping',
  FUEL_VOUCHER: 'voucher para abastecimento',
  MONTHLY_DISCOUNT: 'desconto na mensalidade',
  CAR_INSURANCE_DISCOUNT: 'voucher para seguro auto',
  PARKING_DISCOUNT: 'voucher para estacionamento',
  FINES_DISCOUNT: 'desconto em multas e debitos',
  IPVA_DISCOUNT: 'voucher para ipva e outros debitos',
  AIRLINE_MILES: 'milhas aereas',
};

export const NAME_TO_ICON: Record<string, string> = {
  [KEY_NAME_TO_ICON.RESCUE_IN_INVOICE]: 'icon-discount',
  [KEY_NAME_TO_ICON.MARKETPLACE]: 'icon-shopping-bag',
  [KEY_NAME_TO_ICON.FUEL_VOUCHER]: 'icon-supply',
  [KEY_NAME_TO_ICON.MONTHLY_DISCOUNT]: 'icon-debit-account',
  [KEY_NAME_TO_ICON.CAR_INSURANCE_DISCOUNT]: 'icon-protect-car',
  [KEY_NAME_TO_ICON.PARKING_DISCOUNT]: 'icon-toll-gate',
  [KEY_NAME_TO_ICON.FINES_DISCOUNT]: 'icon-attach',
  [KEY_NAME_TO_ICON.IPVA_DISCOUNT]: 'icon-vehicle',
  [KEY_NAME_TO_ICON.AIRLINE_MILES]: 'icon-airplane',
};
```

### 3. View Component (view.tsx - simplified)

```typescript
const PointsView: FC<PointsViewProps> = ({
  isLoadingBalance,
  handleGoBack,
  pointsAvailable,
  items,
  onOpenExtract,
  onOpenDefault,
  modalizeRef,
  isMyOrders,
  setIsMyOrders,
  onMenuPress,
  handleMyOrders,
}) => {
  return (
    <>
      <BasicScreen
        errorButtonOnPress={() => {}}
        hasScroll
        leftIconOnPress={() => {
          isMyOrders ? setIsMyOrders(false) : handleGoBack();
        }}
        rightIcon="icon-menu"
        rightIconOnPress={onMenuPress}
        hasRightIcon={!isMyOrders}
        title={isMyOrders ? 'Meu espaço' : 'Programa de Pontos'}
      >
        {isMyOrders ? (
          <CardActivity
            isLoading={isLoadingBalance}
            icon="icon-shopping-bag"
            showIcon
            showIconRight={false}
            hideBackground
            hideBorder
            title="Meus pedidos"
            titleTextType="paragraphXL"
            onPress={handleMyOrders}
          />
        ) : (
          <Box ml="smaller" mr="smaller">
            <CardPoints
              icon="icon-benefits"
              iconInfo="icon-help"
              iconAction="icon-next"
              isLoading={isLoadingBalance}
              mt="smaller"
              mb="xs"
              onPressIconInfo={onOpenDefault}
              onPressExtract={() => onOpenExtract()}
              textExtract="Extrato completo"
              title="Pontos disponíveis"
              valuePoints={formatPoints(pointsAvailable ?? 0)}
            />

            <Text type="paragraphXXXL" mb="xxxs">
              Onde usar meus pontos
            </Text>

            <CardMiddle
              items={items as PropsCardMiddle['items']}
              renderType="grid"
              isLoading={isLoadingBalance}
              mb="xs"
            />

            <LearnMorePointsSection />
          </Box>
        )}
      </BasicScreen>
      <PointsInfoBottomSheet modalizeRef={modalizeRef} />
    </>
  );
};
```

### 4. Store Models

```typescript
// PointsProduct
export interface PointsProduct {
  name: string;
  redemptionOrigin?: string;
  convertionFactor?: number;
  minRedemptionValue?: number;
  productCode?: string;
  campaingId?: string;
  conversionFactor?: number;
  icon?: string;
  code?: string;
  origin?: string;
  points?: number;
  action?: string | null;
  campaignId?: string | null;
}

// PointsBalanceState
export interface PointsBalanceState {
  points?: number;
  status: PointsBalanceStatus;
  error?: string;
}

// ParameterPointsProgramState
export interface ParameterPointsProgramState {
  data?: ParameterPointsProgramResponse[];
  selectedCategory?: ParameterPointsProgramResponse;
  status: ParameterPointsProgramStatus;
  pointsQuantity: number;
  conversionFactor: number;
}
```

### 5. Utility Function

